https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/wiki/Table#debugging

For debug drawing one needs to create `ShapeRenderer`, and call `shapeRenderer.setAutoShapeType(true);`

So debug drawing code now looks like:

``` java
shapeRenderer.begin();
table.drawDebug(shapeRenderer);
shapeRenderer.end();
```

But I am lazy and don't want to edit wiki

